{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"0cdd33cc-65f0-4b40-b3f1-82d551fc0bdc","content":"Two things change with xUnit v3 + MTP:\n\n**1. Filter syntax** — MTP uses `--filter` but with a different expression language. The VSTest `~` (contains) operator becomes `=~` and `&` becomes `&`:\n\n```bash\n# Old (VSTest)\ndotnet test --filter \"FullyQualifiedName~IntegrationTests&Category=Smoke\"\n\n# New (MTP)\ndotnet test --filter \"FullyQualifiedName=~IntegrationTests&Category=Smoke\"\n```\n\nNote `=~` (regex/contains match) replaces `~`.\n\n**2. `[Trait]` → `[Category]`** — xUnit v3 dropped `Trait(\"Category\", …\")` in favor of `[Category(\"…\")]` from `System.ComponentModel`. Your test file needs updating:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_017NkzzkxTkCp1LeNs7ogGdu","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-5dc42768f88e456b91ed523e7bcc8a8a/IntegrationTests.cs","old_str":"using Xunit;\n\nnamespace MyApp.Tests;\n\n[Trait(\"Category\", \"Smoke\")]","new_str":"using System.ComponentModel;\nusing Xunit;\n\nnamespace MyApp.Tests;\n\n[Category(\"Smoke\")]"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-5dc42768f88e456b91ed523e7bcc8a8a/IntegrationTests.cs."}],"interactionId":"b240de21-9a34-4859-9042-ef56f611c9a9","outputTokens":369,"requestId":"042D:11F7A2:1F73866:234CA4F:69E81B65"},"id":"244a6c31-081e-44d9-8aab-e8e77d8eca79","timestamp":"2026-04-22T00:50:54.726Z","parentId":"1bd4ea5b-8e9e-44ba-9e74-0b05c9ba8315"}
